***************Introduction***********
1.It is used to develop web application
2.SPA- Single Page Application -->
--It has one body and one head
--does not load every time.
example-Gmail,FaceBook,Ganna.com,GitHub
--Increase performance.
3.index.html -->head file.
4.MPA - Multiple Page Application. -->
ReactJs,VueJs
example-Amazon

*************History Of Angular***********
--combines module,declaration,services with the web.

******************Version******************
AngularJS--> 1.x.x
1-major version
x- minor version
x-patch 


1.AngularJS--
--Oct 2010. 

2.Version2
--September 14, 2016.

3.version4 
--On 13 December 2016 Angular 4 was announced, skipping 3 to avoid a confusion due to the 
  misalignment of the router package's version
--Angular 4 March 23, 2017

**Features in version 4.3
--Introducing HttpClient, a smaller, easier to use, and more powerful library for making HTTP Requests.
--New router life cycle events.

4.version5
--Angular 5  November 1, 2017.
--Key improvements in Angular 5 include improvements related to Material Design.
--Angular Material comprises a range of components which implement common interaction 
  patterns according to the Material Design specification.  
  
5.version6
Angular 6 may, 2018
- It was a major relaese which provides some features like: ng update, ng add, Angular Elements, Angular Material 
+ CDK Components, Angular Material Starter Components, CLI Workspaces
- Animations Performance Improvements, and RxJS v6.

6.Angular 7 October 18, 2018
- Updates regarding Application Performance
Angular Material & CDK
- Virtual Scrolling
- Improved Accessibility of Selects
- Supports Content Projection using web standard for custom elements
- Dependency updates regarding TypeScript 3.1, RxJS 6.3, Node 10

7. Angular 8 May 28 2019

8.Angular 9 February 7 2020


**********************Angular Architecture************************
--view-->to display end user info
--component-->to process the data , to write busibess logic



1.component-->require 4 files
1.HTML File -->to display view on browser
2.CSS File -->Styling purpose
3.TS File -->Business Logic
4.Spec.ts File -->Testing File
